## Development

### Adding Routes

Routes are file-based in `src/routes/`:
- `index.tsx` → `/`
- `about.tsx` → `/about`
- `users/$userId.tsx` → `/users/:userId`
- `_authenticated/dashboard.tsx` → `/dashboard` (with auth guard)

### Adding UI Components

```bash
pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add button card input
```

### API Integration

Query options are defined in `src/lib/api-client.ts`:

```tsx
import { useQuery } from '@tanstack/react-query';
import { userQueryOptions } from '@/lib/api-client';

function MyComponent() {
  const { data } = useQuery(userQueryOptions('123'));
}
```

